dc_title_s: Norfolciae descriptio: The description of Norfolk; Amstelodami, apud Ioannem Ianssonium.; Description of Norfolk
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Ships and a sea monster are in the ocean. Title cartouche includes fruit and a face. This state was publshed in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1636 and 1637. From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 37 x 47 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664.,Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664. Appendix Atlas.,Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner.
